		<div class="phone-veri-header">
			<a href=""></a>
		</div>
		<div class="phone-veri-login">
			<div class="phone-veri-list">
				<label>手机号：</label>
				<input type="text" class="phone-veri-num" placeholder="请输入手机号">
			</div>
			<div class="phone-veri-list phone-veri-flex">
				<input type="text" class="phone-veri-code" placeholder="验证码">
				<a href="" class="btn btn-success">输入验证码</a>
				<span class="phone-veri-right" style="display:block;"></span>
			</div>
			<div class="phone-veri-list phone-veri-flex">
				<input type="text" class="phone-veri-code" placeholder="验证码">
				<a href="" class="btn btn-disable">23s以后重发</a>
				<span class="phone-veri-right"></span>
			</div>
			<div class="phone-veri-code-tips" style="display:block;"><p>如无法接收验证码，请重启手机并确认短信未被拦截！4G用户请关闭4G网络进行接收！</p></div>
			<div class="phone-veri-list">
				<label>设置密码：</label>
				<input type="password" class="phone-veri-num" placeholder="6-18位字母、符号或数字">
			</div>
			<p class="phone-veri-tips">点击立即购物，表示您同意丰趣海淘<a href="">《服务协议》</a></p>
			<div class="phone-veri-submit">
				<a href="" class="btn btn-success btn-big">立即购物</a>
			</div>
			<p class="phone-veri-login-btn">已有丰趣海淘账号？<a href="">请登录</a></p>
		</div>
	</div>
